(9, 1, '2012-04-22 12:00:34', '2012-04-22 04:00:34', 'The Switch is a leader in the brain, learning, thinking, creativity and memory field. We are committed in delivering innovation and creativity solutions to the challenges and needs of the future, especially in the knowledge based industry era. The Switch collaborates with its clients to help them gain competitive advantage through developing high performance individuals who synergize with their business strategy.\r\n\r\nUsing our research, industry and business process knowledge, we provide education, training, consultation, facilitation and special events management through mental development, creativity, thinking, learning skills and intellectual capital development.\r\n\r\nWe bring together proven strategic planning approaches, practical methods for organizational effectiveness and the best tools to enable creativity, thinking and learning mind sets.', 'Company Profile', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'company-profile', '', '', '2012-04-22 12:22:48', '2012-04-22 04:22:48', '', 6, 'http://localhost/ideaspark/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
